I have a dinner party tonight.

55
00:05:28,810 --> 00:05:30,040
Have your own dinner.

56
00:05:31,580 --> 00:05:35,670
[Jinhai High School]

57
00:05:56,860 --> 00:05:57,740
Stop.

58
00:05:59,290 --> 00:06:00,250
Which class are you from?

59
00:06:00,340 --> 00:06:01,220
I...

60
