Okay.

62
00:06:04,570 --> 00:06:05,650
Let me see the surveillance.

63
00:06:06,890 --> 00:06:08,050
You don't need it, right?

64
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:10,050
Ms Wang.

65
00:06:10,140 --> 00:06:12,280
The road is being repaired
near my home today.

66
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:13,170
Li Jin Bu.

67
00:06:13,260 --> 00:06:14,450
Please respect me.

68
00:06:14,540 --> 00:06:15,850
Please make up a new excuse next time.

69
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,780
This time,

70
00:06:18,740 --> 00:06:19,810
