206
00:11:58,940 --> 00:12:00,920
of this combination.

207
00:12:01,180 --> 00:12:02,480
Do you have one that you don't eat?

208
00:12:03,380 --> 00:12:05,170
I don't want chilli, onion,
ginger, garlic and cilantro.

209
00:12:19,220 --> 00:12:20,810
A bowl of wonton, please.

210
00:12:20,900 --> 00:12:22,130
Okay, please hold on a second.

211
00:12:27,580 --> 00:12:28,880
I don't want it. Sorry.

212
00:12:29,260 --> 00:12:30,140
I have...

213
00:12:42,220 --> 00:12:45,490
I can skip the botox.

214
00:12:45,580 --> 00:12:48,570
But I have to find out more
about this sculptra.

215
00:12:48,660 --> 00:12:49,850
Please take a look.

216
00:12:49,940 --> 00:12:50,850
Get up.

217
00:12:51,090 --> 00:12:51,970
Li Qing Tong.

218
00:12:52,430 --> 00:12:53,310
Get up.

219
00:12:54,060 --> 00:12:56,650
There is a discount.

220
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:00,050
Come in.

221
00:13:00,130 --> 00:13:01,200
Where is the waiter?

222
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,930
Please turn the light on.

223
00:13:04,020 --> 00:13:05,010
Please.

224
00:13:06,860 --> 00:13:07,890
Don't vomit.

225
00:13:10,380 --> 00:13:11,970
Please turn on all the lights.

226
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,660
[Jinhai]

227
00:13:17,660 --> 00:13:18,570
Why do you apologize?

228
00:13:18,860 --> 00:13:21,890
I made a farce at the
parent-teacher conference yesterday.

229
00:13:21,980 --> 00:13:22,770
In fact,

230
00:13:22,860 --> 00:13:23,850
as you can see,

231
00:13:23,940 --> 00:13:25,810
I didn't attend Fudan.

232
00:13:25,900 --> 00:13:28,250
I just want to pretend.

233
00:13:28,730 --> 00:13:31,480
I am afraid that it will affect my child.

234
00:13:31,570 --> 00:13:35,410
Classmates and teachers
will make fun of her.

235
00:13:35,620 --> 00:13:36,650
You can be assured.

236
00:13:36,740 --> 00:13:38,770
The school will never let this happen.

237
00:13:38,850 --> 00:13:39,970
Thank you.

238
00:13:40,050 --> 00:13:40,570
Thank you.

239
00:13:40,660 --> 00:13:41,330
Thank you.

240
00:13:41,420 --> 00:13:42,330
I can understand

241
00:13:42,740 --> 00:13:44,560
all that you said.

242
00:13:44,780 --> 00:13:45,970
But I think it is imperative

243
00:13:46,060 --> 00:13:48,050
to address the situation
of Li Jin Bu today.

244
00:13:48,310 --> 00:13:49,130
What's wrong?

245
00:13:49,220 --> 00:13:50,280
So you don't know.

246
00:13:50,610 --> 00:13:52,410
She didn't come to school today.

247
00:13:53,690 --> 00:13:54,810
She sent me a message

248
00:13:54,900 --> 00:13:56,290
saying she wished the school would expel her.

249
00:13:56,380 --> 00:13:58,000
Then she stopped replying to my messages.

250
00:14:01,100 --> 00:14:02,450
Why?

251
00:14:02,860 --> 00:14:03,850
Fan Shui Shui.

252
00:14:04,020 --> 00:14:05,130
Do you get in touch with her?

253
00:14:05,220 --> 00:14:06,090
She doesn't reply to messages.

254
00:14:06,180 --> 00:14:07,230
She doesn't answer her phone.

255
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:09,490
Why doesn't she even answer your phone?

256
00:14:11,180 --> 00:14:11,770
When I find her,

257
00:14:11,850 --> 00:14:13,690
I have to educate her.

258
00:14:19,540 --> 00:14:22,080
Where do you think she's been?

259
00:14:22,850 --> 00:14:25,210
[She wouldn't have gone
to Chen Jun He, would she?]

260
00:14:30,180 --> 00:14:31,320
It's not possible.

261
00:14:32,940 --> 00:14:33,450
She

262
00:14:33,530 --> 00:14:34,330
doesn't know anything.

263
00:14:34,410 --> 00:14:35,610
Where can she find him?

264
00:14:35,700 --> 00:14:37,050
[If not, let's call the police.]

265
00:14:37,140 --> 00:14:38,450
[Just in case.]

266
00:14:39,010 --> 00:14:39,890
[Tong.]

267
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:40,530
[Tong?]

268
00:14:40,620 --> 00:14:41,500
No need.

269
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:43,180
I found her.

270
00:14:47,610 --> 00:14:48,490
Li Jin Bu.

271
00:14:55,020 --> 00:14:56,840
Why did you ask the teacher to expel you?

272
00:14:58,170 --> 00:14:59,050
I don't want to go to school.

273
00:15:00,140 --> 00:15:01,250
You're only seventeen.

274
00:15:01,340 --> 00:15:02,690
What do you want to do
if you don't go to school?

275
00:15:02,780 --> 00:15:03,760
Do whatever.

276
00:15:04,260 --> 00:15:05,250
Enough.

277
00:15:05,330 --> 00:15:06,210
Don't mess around here.

278
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:08,840
I'll be eighteen soon.

279
00:15:09,220 --> 00:15:10,160
I'll be an adult soon.

280
00:15:10,370 --> 00:15:11,970
I can make my own decisions, right?

281
00:15:12,130 --> 00:15:13,010
I don't need your attention.

282
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:14,210
You'll be eighteen soon.

283
00:15:14,300 --> 00:15:16,250
So you don't need me anymore, do you?

284
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:20,180
Why didn't you say that
when you were eight years old?

285
00:15:20,270 --> 00:15:22,290
Why didn't you say that
when I gave birth to you?

286
00:15:22,370 --> 00:15:23,090
I'd rather tell you

287
